OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FA woman who told police that Noah
OL,8,FDonohoe had been injected with heroin
OL,9,For naloxone prior to his death later
OL,10,Fsaid this was a "rumour" and she had
OL,11,Fno information about how he
OL,12,Fdisappeared, an inquest has heard.
OL,14,FThe inquest into the death of Noah at
OL,15,FBelfast Coroner's Court, which is
OL,16,Fbeing heard with a jury, is in its
OL,17,F12th week.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
