FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, it heard evidence from a
OL,8,Fwoman who was convicted of handling
OL,9,Fstolen goods in 2021 after being found
OL,10,Fto be in possession of his laptop at
OL,11,Fher accommodation near the Donohoe
OL,12,Ffamily home.
OL,14,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,15,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,16,Fin the storm drain tunnel in north
OL,17,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,18,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,19,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,20,Fcity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,8,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,10,FThe inquest was previously told there
OL,11,Fwas no toxicological evidence he was
OL,12,Funder the influence of drugs at the
OL,13,Ftime of his death but it could not be
OL,14,Fstated with absolute certainty.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, the jury heard evidence
OL,17,Ffrom Maria Nolan about she came into
OL,18,Fpossession of Noah's laptop, as well
OL,19,Fas statements she had provided to
OL,20,Fpolice in the past.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FMs Nolan told the inquest that a man
OL,8,Fshe knew, Daryl Paul, told her that he
OL,9,Fhad a laptop that he could sell at
OL,10,FCash Converters to raise money to buy
OL,11,Fdrugs on June 24 2020.
OL,13,FThe laptop was Noah's, and was part of
OL,14,Fseveral items that had gone missing `
OL,15,Fincluding his backpack and coat.
OL,17,FShe said she did not know about Noah
OL,18,For his disappearance at the time and
OL,19,Fbelieved the laptop was owned by Mr
OL,20,FPaul, whom she accompanied.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FThe inquest heard Cash Converters
OL,8,Fwould not accept the laptop without a
OL,9,Fcharger, and the store later raised
OL,10,Fsuspicions about the computer with
OL,11,Fpolice.
OL,13,FMs Nolan had taken possession of the
OL,14,Flaptop after the encounter when she
OL,15,Fparted ways with Mr Paul, who was
OL,16,Flater arrested by police.
OL,18,FPolice then found the laptop in Ms
OL,19,FNolan's room at Queen's Quarter
OL,20,FHousing on University Street, which is
OL,21,Facross the road from the Donohoe home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FMr Paul, who the jury was told was
OL,8,Fregularly outside Queen's Quarter
OL,9,FHousing, was also convicted in
OL,10,Frelation to Noah's stolen laptop.
OL,12,FMs Nolan said she would describe Mr
OL,13,FPaul as a friend and told the inquest
OL,14,Fthey were not boyfriend and girlfriend.
OL,16,FBrenda Campbell KC, for Noah's mother
OL,17,FFiona, said her client had found it
OL,18,Fvery disconcerting that the laptop had
OL,19,Fended up in the possession of people
OL,20,Fwho were so nearby.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
