PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FPrevious statements and records of
OL,8,Fpolice interviews with the witness
OL,9,Fwere read to the jury by counsel to
OL,10,Fthe coroner Peter Coll KC.
OL,12,FIn one of those statements which she
OL,13,Fhad prepared following consultation
OL,14,Fwith the Donohoe family's legal team,
OL,15,FMs Nolan said she was aware of "how
OL,16,FNoah was injected with heroin or
OL,17,Fnaloxone as he travelled through"
OL,18,FBelfast city centre.
OL,26,@wD@`OUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
