OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FShe said that she had previously seen
OL,8,Faddicts targeting vulnerable or
OL,9,Felderly people and robbing them and
OL,10,Fthat "this is what happened to Noah".
OL,12,FShe said that she had spoken to people
OL,13,Fin a "tight-knit" addict community
OL,14,Fwhere it had been mentioned that Noah
OL,15,Fhad been injected with heroin or
OL,16,Fnaloxone, and that a secret of this
OL,17,Fnature would be openly confided within
OL,18,Fthis group.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@dO]uD@FOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FHowever, in a later police interview
OL,8,Fas well as a statement directly to the
OL,9,Finquest and her evidence in front of
OL,10,Fthe jury, Ms Nolan said she did not
OL,11,Fknow this to be fact.
OL,13,FShe said she did not write the
OL,14,Fstatement and felt under pressure to
OL,15,Fsign it, adding that she thought she
OL,16,Fwas helping the family.
OL,18,FShe said she never wanted to put
OL,19,Fforward that she knew for a fact what
OL,20,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
