OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FShe said the only thing she had
OL,8,Finformation on was the laptop, adding:
OL,9,F"I don't know nothing else."
OL,11,FMs Nolan also said she saw a green
OL,12,Fcoat, with characteristics similar to
OL,13,FNoah's, in Mr Paul's home at the time
OL,14,Fhe picked up the laptop to sell it.
OL,16,FHowever, she reiterated she did not
OL,17,Fknow about Noah or his missing items
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
