FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FMs Nolan said she had first heard the
OL,8,Frumour of Noah being injected when she
OL,9,Fwas assaulted by a woman in August who
OL,10,Fasked if she had "done it".
OL,12,FShe also said the she had not seen
OL,13,FNoah be robbed or attacked or heard
OL,14,Fanyone make any confessions to that
OL,15,Feffect.
OL,17,FMs Noah said she had never seen
OL,18,Fsomeone inject or threaten to inject
OL,19,Fsomeone with heroin, but it was a fear
OL,20,Fshe had herself.
OL,26,@rD@ROUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
