OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FShe told police no one had put
OL,8,Fpressure on her to make her statements.
OL,10,FIn a later statement to the inquest,
OL,11,FMs Nolan said she never met or knew
OL,12,FNoah and did not know how he died.
OL,14,F"I have heard rumours and speculation
OL,15,Flike many people have but the reality
OL,16,Fis I do not know if there is any truth
OL,17,Fto these rumours."
OL,19,FShe later added: "I don't know what
OL,20,Fhappened to Noah."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@RO]{D@ROU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
