FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FUnder questioning from Ms Campbell, Ms
OL,8,FNolan said police came to seize the
OL,9,Flaptop from her accommodation the
OL,10,Fnight or two nights after she came to
OL,11,Fhave it.
OL,13,FThe witness said the police had not
OL,14,Fasked her about Noah, about how he was
OL,15,Fstill missing, or his other missing
OL,16,Fitems at the time.
OL,18,FShe said they had told her she had a
OL,19,Flaptop to do with a "high-profile
OL,20,Fcase" but did not ask how she got it,
OL,21,Fnor mention Noah's name.
OL,26,@{D@UOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FShe said she was confused about the
OL,8,Fsituation and found out the connection
OL,9,Flater on, and made attempts to contact
OL,10,Fpolice "to see what was going on".
OL,12,FHowever, she said she had problems
OL,13,Fwith her memory due to drug use at the
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FAsked by Donal Lunny KC, for the PSNI,
OL,17,Fif it would have meant anything to her
OL,18,Fif police had mentioned Noah's name,
OL,19,Fshe said she would not have known what
OL,20,Fthey were talking about.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
