PN,44915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FAlso asked by Ms Campbell about
OL,8,Fevidence relating to another witness
OL,9,Fwho said Ms Nolan had previously been
OL,10,Fin Noah's company, she disputed this
OL,11,Fand said she had never met the boy.
OL,13,FMs Nolan said she had previously been
OL,14,F"hammered" by the press and public,
OL,15,Fadding she was "horrified" that the
OL,16,Flaptop belonged to Noah.
OL,18,FShe said she had been threatened,
OL,19,Fphysically assaulted, and abused over
OL,20,Fthe matter.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@JO]wD@POUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
