PN,44916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777065070
OL,3,CWoman told police 'rumour' Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe was injected with heroin,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FShe said she was now clean from drugs
OL,8,Fand attending counselling.
OL,10,F"I feel desperately sad for Noah's
OL,11,Fmummy, I hope she gets answers."
OL,13,FThe inquest will resume on Thursday.
